Field Documentation

UInt32 Bsp_VidDecChipIdParams::deviceNum

Device number for which chip ID is required.

Device number will be 0 in most cases, unless multiple devices are cascaded together like in TVP5158 in which case device num can be from 0 .. Bsp_VidDecCreateParams.numDevicesAtPort - 1
